The following steps should be implemented in order, 
1) Open the GitHub Repository called: Turtlebot_Burger 
2) Git clone the Repository and do “catkin_make” 
3) Connect the ESP32 bluetooth to the PC.   
4) Run the following command: sudo rfcomm bind rfcomm1 "Address of Device on Bluetooth"  
5) Run the following command to launch the Project: 
6) roslaunch turtlebot3_project_launch project.launch (The Launch file will launch 
everything)
